dct_title_s: Coast of Africa from the Straits of Gibraltar to Cabo Verde
dct_description_sm: Appears in: Untitled atlas containing maps of Africa (1803)

Part of a series of four double-page coastal maps, (see NOR 227, NOR 0329, NOR 0330, NOR
        0331). Coastline contains soundings; Prime meridian through Greenwich. Top right: Chart
        1.
